title: Volvo car sales in Sweden 2009 to 2019
summary: In general Units sold has rose over the Year.
Units sold is gradually increasing from 2014 to 2015, roughly constant from 2015 to 2016, and lastly roughly decreasing from 2016 to 2018.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Units sold, about 75506.0 was reported at Year 2017
The lowest Units sold, of value 61496.0 was reported at Year 2014
